SAL project-wide dependencies:

 * log4j *
log4j can be obtained from http://logging.apache.org/log4j/1.2
Debian/Ubuntu package: liblog4j1.2-java

SAL expects to find the following JAR file:
/usr/share/log4j-1.2.jar


SAL plugin dependencies:

 * Registration with Bonjour *
 SAL requires Avahi4J so agents can register with Bonjour, and clients can
 discover them at run-time. Avahi4J can be found at http://avahi4j.googlecode.com
 
 SAL expects to find the Avahi4J's JAR file in /usr/share/java/avahi4j.jar and
 its JNI library in /usr/lib/jni

 * Serial Endpoint *
requires the GNU implementation of the Java CommAPI from
http://rxtx.qbang.org/wiki/index.php/Main_Page
Also comes as a package in Ubuntu (librxtx-java)

SAL expects to find the following JAR file:
/usr/share/java/RXTXcomm.jar
JNI libs in /usr/lib

 * Simple SNMP endpoint *
requires the WestHawk SNMP from http://snmp.westhawk.co.uk/
This one is still shipped with SAL (in libs) and will be copied to
/usr/share/java/snmp6_0.jar

 * v4l4j protocol *
v4l4j can be obtained from http://v4l4j.googlecode.com/svn/v4l4j/trunk

SAL expects to find the following JAR file:
/usr/share/java/v4l4j.jar

JNI lib in /usr/lib/jni

 * HAL helper *
requires the HAL package from http://sal.googlecode.com/svn/HAL/trunk

SAL expects to find the following JAR file:
/usr/share/java/HAL.jar

JNI lib in /usr/lib/jni


